note pyramid.vrb — centered star pyramid.
note Row i has (rows - i) leading spaces and (2*i - 1) stars.

ask the user "how many rows?" and save to rows.

row = 1.
while row <= rows:
    sp = 1.
    spaces = rows - row.
    while sp <= spaces:
        display " ".
        sp += 1.
    end.
    stars = row * 2 - 1.
    col = 1.
    while col <= stars:
        display "*".
        col += 1.
    end.
    say.
    row += 1.
end.
